Third Workshop on Seeking Low‑Dimensionality in Deep Neural Networks
January 2023, MBZUAI

Schedule

Tuesday, January 3
Welcome Session and Educational Tutorials
  • The first tutorial will be on recent progress in low-dimensional models for high-dimensional data, based on an ICASSP 2022 short course.
  • The second tutorial will be on sparse and self-expressive deep neural networks, led by Atlas Wang and Chong You.
